<div class="glass-card content-card reveal">

<h2>👩‍💻 Member 1 Reflection</h2>

<h3>Vaishnavi Sanjay Kadam</h3>

<p>
During the development of the NLP Knowledge Artifact Repository, I learned
various concepts of Natural Language Processing such as text preprocessing,
sentence segmentation, tokenization, stemming, lemmatization, TF-IDF,
word embeddings, language models, and transformer architectures.
</p>

<p>
Researching these topics helped me understand how machines process human
language and convert raw text into meaningful information. I explored
different NLP applications including chatbots, machine translation,
sentiment analysis, spam detection, and text summarization.
</p>

<p>
This project also improved my research skills, content organization,
technical documentation abilities, and understanding of Artificial
Intelligence technologies. Designing educational content for a website
helped me learn how to present technical information in a structured,
professional, and user-friendly format.
</p>

<p>
Working collaboratively enhanced my communication and teamwork skills.
Overall, this project strengthened my academic knowledge and increased
my interest in advanced NLP and AI technologies.
</p>

<hr>

<p><strong>Name:</strong> Vaishnavi Sanjay Kadam</p>
<p><strong>Roll No:</strong> 36</p>
<p><strong>PRN:</strong> 124BTCM1013</p>
<p><strong>Division:</strong> TYCM2</p>

</div>

<div class="glass-card content-card reveal">

<h2>👨‍💻 Member 2 Reflection</h2>

<h3>Maher Dhami</h3>

<p>
Through this project, I gained valuable knowledge about Natural Language
Processing and its growing importance in modern Artificial Intelligence.
I learned about feature extraction techniques, language representation,
embeddings, transformer models, and recent innovations such as BERT,
GPT, Large Language Models, and Retrieval-Augmented Generation.
</p>

<p>
Creating workflow diagrams and comparison tables helped me understand
the practical implementation of NLP systems and how different techniques
are used to solve language-related problems. I also improved my skills
in website organization, information visualization, and technical
presentation.
</p>

<p>
The project provided hands-on experience in collaborative development,
planning, content management, and quality assurance. It taught me the
importance of combining theoretical understanding with practical
implementation while developing educational resources.
</p>

<p>
Overall, this experience enhanced both my technical knowledge and
teamwork abilities while giving me deeper insight into modern AI-driven
language technologies.
</p>

<hr>

<p><strong>Name:</strong> Maher Dhami</p>
<p><strong>Roll No:</strong> 20</p>
<p><strong>PRN:</strong> 124BTCM1120</p>
<p><strong>Division:</strong> TYCM2</p>

